# Kwalify Creative North Star (required)

Before proposing or implementing any design, UI, scene, animation, or visual change, read and comply with:

`docs/KWALIFY_CREATIVE_NORTH_STAR.md`

That document overrides other docs when they conflict. See `docs/DOCUMENT_HIERARCHY.md`.

Core checks:
- Playlist is the primary product; visuals support feeling only
- UX loop: HOME → TYPE MOMENT → MAKE PLAYLIST → RESULT (no interruptions)
- Emotional Editorial Worlds with dream-object anchors — not cinematic realism
- Phase 1 art: `petrol_station_2am` only until style is locked
- Motion: fades/opacity only — no camera systems or staged loaders
- If a feature does not improve 5-second clarity or 30-second "it gets me", do not prioritise it
